00:22:16.110 --> 00:22:18.110
And it's like, okay, hold on to 
this...

00:22:18.148 --> 00:22:20.148
[ Laughter ]

00:22:22.006 --> 00:22:24.006
&gt;&gt;  But I haven't done it since 
