of that stratification.

00:35:01.845 --> 00:35:03.922
&gt;&gt;  That's a very good point.  
Yeah.  That's great.

00:35:09.636 --> 00:35:11.700
&gt;&gt;  I did -- I was able to do 
some workshops.  When you said 

00:35:11.701 --> 00:35:13.701
that, yeah, I did do that.

00:35:17.229 --> 00:35:20.069
And it was the Queens Library.  
I was very popular in February 

00:35:20.070 --> 00:35:22.114
and March.
[ Laughter ]

00:35:25.807 --> 00:35:28.291
I would get calls, say we have a
