00:35:35.502 --> 00:35:37.502
sometimes there were older 
people, you 

00:35:38.972 --> 00:35:41.228
know, retired people who wanted 
to sit among the 

00:35:41.229 --> 00:35:44.118
eight-year-olds, because they 
